fields.description:
Bathroom storage is strongly included in your daily routines. Properly designed bathroom storage is a working helper. Morning and evening activities are much easier when your important items are in good order and can always be found in their own places!

Bathroom cabinets bring much-needed extra space while keeping your personal belongings out of sight. In addition, they provide protection from splashes and airborne dust.

Bathroom storage offers a wide range of options, from impressive mirror cabinets to large or small open shelves . Wheeled carriages provide practical storage space, especially for smaller bathrooms. You can always move the cart to where space is available as needed.

Bathroom storage offers every home decorator a number of different opportunities to create an entity that emphasizes their own style. Check out our diverse selection and make your bathroom a smoother everyday life!
fields.title: Bathroom storage helps in a smoother everyday life

fields.description:
Bathroom furniture is an integral part of weekday and holiday mornings as well as late evenings. High-quality and well-designed bathroom furniture and toilet furniture make daily routines easier and can even save your day.

By choosing the right furniture for your bathroom, you will make every day smoother. Our collection of bathroom furniture and toilet furniture meets the needs of every user with its high quality.

Here you will find the right bathroom furniture for your home for small and large spaces as well as for one and several users, as well as other necessary bathroom accessories .

In the small bathroom, the compact basin cabinet leaves useful extra space in the room, for example for drying clothes. In a multi-person household, the bathroom's double basin, in turn, speeds up morning activities when the teeth can be brushed two side by side.

Well-designed bathroom furniture and toilet furniture bring efficient storage space to your bathroom. The bathroom's spacious basin cabinet keeps your important belongings in neat order. You’ll find everything quickly and in just the right place, and your morning tasks will run smoothly without unnecessary hurry.

The bathroom furniture in our collection fits elegantly with the other furniture in your bathroom. Take a look at our different options and choose high-quality bathroom furniture to suit your style!
fields.title: Bathroom furniture for better washing in the morning and evening

fields.description:
Bathroom accessories help you to complete a functional and complete interior of your bathroom.

The bathroom has a number of different items for which you need just the right kind of bathroom accessories. In the shower , storage , sink , next to the toilet seat , drying hands ̶ the more you think about it, the more items you will find.

Make it easy to decorate your bathroom and dive into the world of our diverse selection. There you will find several options to suit different styles, each of which has been carefully considered and designed specifically for the bathrooms.

Often, for example, finding functional and stylish interiors suitable for the bathroom has its own challenges, but no longer. Our range includes many inspiring options and best of all, most of our different products complement each other perfectly.

Bathroom accessories will help you to effortlessly complete the bathroom decor of your dreams. Discover and experience for yourself what all our range of bathroom accessories can offer for your interior design. We are sure to find the details that suit your taste and your personal style!
fields.title: Bathroom accessories complete the style of your bathroom

fields.description:
The sink is used daily in your home. It is washed, cleaned and sometimes even played with. When choosing a suitable sink, it is worth considering the sufficient size of the individual sink and the number of users.

If you wash your hands in addition to your hands in the sink, the smallest in the family or pets, you should choose the most spacious sink possible. On the other hand, if just washing your hands is enough, you don't even have to be big in the sink.

In our selection, you will find washbasins that can be installed directly on top of the pool cabinet and basin basins that can be installed on the worktop of the pool cabinet. If there are several people in the same bathroom at the same time brushing their teeth, a practical double basin facilitates daily activities.

You will also find several different types of taps from us . The faucets are designed to fit perfectly with our sinks. You complete the whole with versatile sink accessories . With accessories, you give each sink the personal look it deserves.

Check out the diverse selection to find a new stylish sink for your bathroom!
fields.title: Sink for washing alone or in pairs
